        <h2 class="section-heading">
            <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/oscar-winners">Anatomy of a Scene | Oscar Winners</a>
        </h2>
                    <a class="user-action" href="https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/oscar-winners">
