            <h2 class="headline">
                <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/video/movies/100000005713792/anatomy-of-a-scene-the-shape-of-water.html" data-tracking-index="1" data-rref="">Anatomy of a Scene | ‘The Shape of Water’</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="summary">Guillermo del Toro narrates a sequence from his film featuring Sally Hawkins and Doug Jones. The film received 13 Oscar nominations, including best picture.</p>
            <p class="byline">
                <span class="freshness"><time data-utc-timestamp="1517504806" datetime="1517504806"></time></span>
                                <span class="divider"></span>
